I've simplified the UI directly in `TextToSpeech.tsx`. The voice selector now presents a single list of valid voices, eliminating artificial groupings. The code handles this list correctly. I'll include a note about the multilingual nature of the voices, as requested, to inform the user. The direct voice list streamlines the UI and guarantees that the UI is easy to implement.


